# GitHub sync (MegaCandle)

After finishing a user-requested code change in this repo:

1. Run `git status` and ensure no secrets are staged (`.env`, `MT5 Pass.txt`, `*.db`).
2. Commit with a clear message describing **why**.
3. Push to `origin master` on `https://github.com/Rasher01-cyber/MegaCandle.git`.

Only commit/push when the user asked for changes or explicitly wants GitHub updated. Do not commit broken builds.
